OL,3,CHow much will Starmer's welfare u-turn
OL,4,Ccost him?
OL,6,FThe welfare U-turn is an expensive one.
OL,8,FProtecting existing Pip claimants is
OL,9,Fexpected to cost an extra #1.5bn a
OL,10,Fyear and unfreezing the Universal
OL,11,FCredit Health element and other
OL,12,Fchanges will cost another #1.5bn.
OL,14,FSo this is a #3bn U-turn.
OL,16,FAnd it has to be added to this month's
OL,17,Ffirst u-turn, the one on winter fuel
OL,18,Fpayments. That's thought to have cost
OL,19,Fanother #1.5bn.
