OL,3,CHow much will Starmer's welfare u-turn
OL,4,Ccost him?
OL,6,FSo all in that could be an extra #8bn
OL,7,Fworth of spending that the chancellor
OL,8,Fhad not factored into her Spending
OL,9,FReview.
OL,11,FNo wonder economists think she may be
OL,12,Fforced into making an even bigger u-
OL,13,Fturn and raise taxes.
OL,15,FIf she took that route then an extra
OL,16,Fpenny on the basic rate of income tax
OL,17,Fwould get her most of that eight
OL,18,Fbillion.
OL,20,FAnd all that is before the commitment
OL,21,Fto spend more, a lot more, on defence.
